# Smart Leads Dashboard — Complete Architecture Blueprint

> **Color Theme:** Black backgrounds · White text · Blue accents (`#2563EB` / `#3B82F6`)  
> **Stack:** React + Vite + TailwindCSS · Node.js + Express · MongoDB · Docker

