## 9. Recommended Reusable Components

| Component | Purpose | Props |
|-----------|---------|-------|
| `Button` | All button variants | `variant`, `size`, `loading`, `disabled` |
| `Input` | Form inputs with error display | `label`, `error`, `...register()` spread |
| `Badge` | Status/source chips | `variant: 'status' \| 'source'`, `value` |
| `Modal` | Create/Edit lead modal | `isOpen`, `onClose`, `title`, `children` |
| `Spinner` | Loading indicator | `size`, `color` |
| `Table` | Generic sortable table | `columns`, `data`, `loading`, `emptyState` |
| `Pagination` | Page navigation | `page`, `pages`, `total`, `onPageChange` |
| `EmptyState` | No-data illustration | `title`, `description`, `action` |
| `ErrorState` | API failure fallback | `message`, `onRetry` |
| `LeadStatusBadge` | Color-coded status | `status: LeadStatus` |
| `LeadFilters` | Filter bar (status/source/search) | `filters`, `onChange` |
| `ProtectedRoute` | Auth guard wrapper | `children` |
| `RoleGuard` | Role-specific render guard | `allowedRoles`, `children` |

