---

## Architecture Decision Records (ADRs)

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| Env validation | Zod in `config/env.ts` | Fail-fast on misconfiguration; typed access |
| Async error handling | `asyncHandler` wrapper | Eliminates try/catch boilerplate in every controller |
| Text search | MongoDB `$text` index | Native, no external dependency; sufficient for this scale |
| Token storage | Zustand memory + localStorage | Memory prevents XSS exposure; localStorage enables refresh persistence |
| Query keys | Object-based (all filters) | Auto-invalidation when any filter changes |
| CSV generation | Server-side streaming | Avoids sending full dataset to client; handles large exports |
| Debounce delay | 350ms | Responsive feel without hammering the API |

